FBIS4-21996 "jptot016__l94053" JPRS-TOT-94-016-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 13 April 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Bomb Blast in Hadera Bomb Blast in Hadera 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam Takes Responsibility TA1304084494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0838 GMT 13 Apr 94 TA1304084494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] We have just learned that 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam has assumed responsibility for the Hadera attack. They placed a telephone call to Qol Yisra'el -- that is how brazen they are -- and speaking in Arabic, they made their announcement that 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam assumes responsibility for this attack.
